    "seo_description": "Explore the Yono VIP system architecture. RummyApp Online provides a technical audit of vertex-shader execution, input-event debouncing, and UI geometry.",
    "seo_keywords": "Yono VIP vertex-shader execution, input-event debouncing metrics, touch-matrix audit, Yono VIP system diagnostic",
